OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAlzheimer's drug hailed as 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmomentous breakthrough     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The first drug to slow the destruction 
OL,6, of the brain in Alzheimer's has been   
OL,7, heralded as momentous.                 
OL,9,FThe research breakthrough ends decades 
OL,10,Fof failure and shows a new era of drugs
OL,11,Fto treat Alzheimer's - the most common 
OL,12,Fform of dementia - is possible.        
OL,14,FYet the medicine, lecanemab, has only a
OL,15,Fsmall effect and its impact on people's
OL,16,Fdaily lives is debated.                
OL,18,FAnd the drug works in the early stages 
OL,19,Fof the disease, so most would miss out 
OL,20,Fwithout a revolution in spotting it.   
